---
title: Sesame-Crumbed Chicken & Bacon-Katsu Sauce with Basmati Rice & Creamy Slaw
description: Bacon-Katsu sauce is like the superhero sidekick of Japanese cuisine - bold, flavourful and ready to take your tastebuds on an adventure! Pour it over a golden crumbed chicken dotted with sesame seeds and watch as every bite becomes a delicious thrill ride.
